---
import RootLayout from "@/layouts/Root.astro";
import Nav from "@/components/Nav.astro";
---

<RootLayout title="About">
  <Nav />
  <main class="px-8 md:px-20 lg:px-32 2xl:px-60 py-12">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-serif font-semibold">
      A little story about myself
    </h1>
    <p class="mt-8 lg:text-lg max-w-[100ch]">
      I'm <strong>Yagnik Patel</strong> and I'm a <strong
        >front-end developer</strong
      > based in <strong>Gujarat, India</strong> who is actively working towards
      becoming a fully-fledged full-stack developer. I am a <strong
        >first-year</strong
      > college student. I plan to try <strong>freelancing</strong> or remote
      jobs to gain practical experience in the industry.
    </p>
    <p class="mt-4 lg:text-lg max-w-[100ch]">
      I had some extra time during the Covid-19 pandemic, so I started learning
      web development. I mainly focus on front-end development, but I also like
      to explore back-end topics to learn more. Because of my schoolwork, I can
      only spend a little time learning. I built this website to share my work,
      and you can reach me through Twitter or email.
    </p>
    <div class="flex gap-8">
      <a
        class="flex space-x-2 items-center group text-neutral-800 hover:underline underline-offset-4 lg:text-lg font-medium rounded-lg mt-6 w-fit"
        href="/projects"
      >
        <span class="group-hover:italic">Projects</span>
        <svg
          xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
          fill="none"
          viewBox="0 0 24 24"
          stroke-width="1.5"
          stroke="currentColor"
          class="w-6 h-6 origin-left group-hover:scale-x-150 transition"
        >
          <path
            stroke-linecap="round"
            stroke-linejoin="round"
            d="M17.25 8.25L21 12m0 0l-3.75 3.75M21 12H3"></path>
        </svg>
      </a>
      <a
        class="flex space-x-2 items-center group text-neutral-800 hover:underline underline-offset-4 lg:text-lg font-medium rounded-lg mt-6 w-fit"
        href="/blog"
      >
        <span class="group-hover:italic">Blogs</span>
        <svg
          xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
          fill="none"
          viewBox="0 0 24 24"
          stroke-width="1.5"
          stroke="currentColor"
          class="w-6 h-6 origin-left group-hover:scale-x-150 transition"
        >
          <path
            stroke-linecap="round"
            stroke-linejoin="round"
            d="M17.25 8.25L21 12m0 0l-3.75 3.75M21 12H3"></path>
        </svg>
      </a>
    </div>
    <div class="flex gap-2 items-center mt-12 flex-wrap">
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-serif font-semibold">My prefered stacks</h1>
      <p>
        (* I have experience with other technologies too, but I like working
        with these tech stacks. *)
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="space-y-4 mt-6">
      <div class="space-y-3">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-medium">Fullstack App</h2>
        <p class="lg:text-lg">
          Nextjs &bull; Auth.js(NextAuth) &bull; Tailwind CSS w. shadcn/ui
          &bull; Database with ORM (Supabase, Prisma, Drizzle)
        </p>
        <p class="lg:text-lg">
          SvelteKit &bull; Auth.js &bull; Tailwind CSS w. shadcn-svelte &bull;
          Database with ORM (Supabase, Prisma, Drizzle)
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="space-y-3">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-medium">Static Site</h2>
        <p class="lg:text-lg">Astro &bull; Tailwind CSS</p>
        <p class="lg:text-lg">
          Vite &bull; HTML &bull; CSS or Tailwind CSS &bull; Javascript
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</RootLayout>
